{"tid":2177944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【臨時論壇】楊岳橋 vs 岑敖暉","createTime":"2020-08-28T05:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T22:39:13.000Z","uid":59066,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"360ab0c62ead54300bf18fb7e7188a08dc053c1a","tid":2177944,"uid":59066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T05:19:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ON4VbXR1i3E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FON4VbXR1i3E&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONiHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=492affd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ON4VbXR1i3E</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對住楊岳橋做選舉論壇<br />\n<span class=\"red\">呢個畫面，有冇似曾相識？</span><br />\n<br />\n當年投咗佢，相信香港「有險可守」、話今次選佢入去先，下次先再投梁天琦嘅人<br />\n<span class=\"red\">又有冇後悔？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然岑敖暉喺片段中略顯緊張同青澀<br />\n但嗰種赤子之心、堅信自己所擁護嘅價值<br />\n每一句都感覺到佢&lsquo;<span class=\"red\">真係好撚鍾意香港</span>&rsquo;<br />\n唔知點解 會有種莫名嘅感染力<br />\n因為我哋真係已經退無可退 <br />\n先會想諗所謂破局<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從來<br />\n人大委任就係一件唔okay 嘅事情<br />\n幾時開始，我哋諗嘅竟然係泛民要去或留<br />\n而唔係堅決反對中共破壞香港法治、剝奪我哋嘅選舉權利？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想借用朱凱迪喺片段最後嗰句：「我哋寧願係戰死沙場，都好過鬱鬱而終。」<br />\n送俾仲玩緊語言偽術，留戀緊初選結果嘅泛民議員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">In a mad world only the mad are sane.</span></span>"},{"pid":"1e1022eb7050b3621f0e283825b0cebbb25c8b66","tid":2177944,"uid":278587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:14:49.000Z","msg":"個論壇的形式好好, 但無奈個時間實在太短啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394a5512e159f3493e76e99ebc9ee44dc95f753a","tid":2177944,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T22:39:13.000Z","msg":"兩個口罩人"}]}